WEBVTT

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:34.200
True and strong relationships
are what you need to fly high

00:03:34.200 --> 00:03:36.960
and make your dreams come true.

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:41.240
My life and probably my career, too,
are a living example of this.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:43.360
Roohi and Yash,

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:51.020
as you grow up, you will realize
that the world puts labels on people.

00:03:51.020 --> 00:03:56.370
Race, color, creed, religion,
wealth, orientation.

00:03:56.370 --> 00:03:59.960
but being different
does not mean being wrong.